data.description: GREAT NEW PRICRE!!!! Welcome to this wonderful 2 story home in a family friendly community, close to schools, shopping and the freeway! This home features 1,993 sqft of living which includes 4 bedrooms and 3 baths with one of each on the main level which is perfect for A guest room. Let's not forget that this home also features an open floor plan with a low maintenance backyard. Now let's get some cardio going and walk up these stairs! Now the second level includes 3 bedrooms, 2 baths, an office space and laundry unit. The Master bedroom comes with its own restroom, his and her's sink, walk in shower and bathtub. COME CHECK ME OUT!!!
